{
  "number": 81,
  "name": "At-Takwir",
  "arabicName": "سُورَةُ التَّكۡوِيرِ",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "totalAyahs": 29,
  "translator": "Saheeh International",
  "edition": "en.sahih",
  "language": "English",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "When the sun is wrapped up [in darkness]",
      "ayah_number": 1,
      "verse_key": "81:1"
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "And when the stars fall, dispersing,",
      "ayah_number": 2,
      "verse_key": "81:2"
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "And when the mountains are removed",
      "ayah_number": 3,
      "verse_key": "81:3"
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "And when full-term she-camels are neglected",
      "ayah_number": 4,
      "verse_key": "81:4"
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "And when the wild beasts are gathered",
      "ayah_number": 5,
      "verse_key": "81:5"
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "And when the seas are filled with flame",
      "ayah_number": 6,
      "verse_key": "81:6"
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "And when the souls are paired",
      "ayah_number": 7,
      "verse_key": "81:7"
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "And when the girl [who was] buried alive is asked",
      "ayah_number": 8,
      "verse_key": "81:8"
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "For what sin she was killed",
      "ayah_number": 9,
      "verse_key": "81:9"
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "And when the pages are made public",
      "ayah_number": 10,
      "verse_key": "81:10"
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "And when the sky is stripped away",
      "ayah_number": 11,
      "verse_key": "81:11"
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "And when Hellfire is set ablaze",
      "ayah_number": 12,
      "verse_key": "81:12"
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "And when Paradise is brought near,",
      "ayah_number": 13,
      "verse_key": "81:13"
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "A soul will [then] know what it has brought [with it].",
      "ayah_number": 14,
      "verse_key": "81:14"
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "So I swear by the retreating stars -",
      "ayah_number": 15,
      "verse_key": "81:15"
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Those that run [their courses] and disappear -",
      "ayah_number": 16,
      "verse_key": "81:16"
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "And by the night as it closes in",
      "ayah_number": 17,
      "verse_key": "81:17"
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "And by the dawn when it breathes",
      "ayah_number": 18,
      "verse_key": "81:18"
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "[That] indeed, the Qur'an is a word [conveyed by] a noble messenger",
      "ayah_number": 19,
      "verse_key": "81:19"
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "[Who is] possessed of power and with the Owner of the Throne, secure [in position],",
      "ayah_number": 20,
      "verse_key": "81:20"
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "Obeyed there [in the heavens] and trustworthy.",
      "ayah_number": 21,
      "verse_key": "81:21"
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "And your companion is not [at all] mad.",
      "ayah_number": 22,
      "verse_key": "81:22"
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "And he has already seen Gabriel in the clear horizon.",
      "ayah_number": 23,
      "verse_key": "81:23"
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "And Muhammad is not a withholder of [knowledge of] the unseen.",
      "ayah_number": 24,
      "verse_key": "81:24"
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "And the Qur'an is not the word of a devil, expelled [from the heavens].",
      "ayah_number": 25,
      "verse_key": "81:25"
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "So where are you going?",
      "ayah_number": 26,
      "verse_key": "81:26"
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "It is not except a reminder to the worlds",
      "ayah_number": 27,
      "verse_key": "81:27"
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "For whoever wills among you to take a right course.",
      "ayah_number": 28,
      "verse_key": "81:28"
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "And you do not will except that Allah wills - Lord of the worlds.",
      "ayah_number": 29,
      "verse_key": "81:29"
    }
  ]
}